## Important Rules

- **One sub-plan at a time** - complete each fully before moving to the next
- **No partial implementations** - each sub-plan must result in working, compilable code
- **No empty commits** - only commit when `git status` shows actual file changes
- **TypeScript strict mode** - no `any` types without justification
- **Tailwind CSS only** - no Bootstrap, no CSS modules, no styled-components
- **React Server Rendering by default** - use `'use client'` only when interactivity requires it

